{"tid":626151,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實要有幾痴線先會認為唔係12碼?","createTime":"2018-04-12T01:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T04:32:01.000Z","uid":25345,"like":72,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"adb5f1fe6ba01bbbfa0807d3c358ab7c5d28d0ce","tid":626151,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9kolwebzNI&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=235\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc9kolwebzNI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D235&d=Pwj1qcM7NItuKhpa9TTTiv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=16bbcba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9kolwebzNI&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=235</a><br />\n<br />\n睇完再睇無數再睇都冇法認為有咩爭議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華斯基斯完全唔知有人係後面,佢成個身準備頂個波<br />\n之後成個人係明顯被撞跌既,唔通你話佢配合後面條友,飛緊過黎既風撞低佢呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aff7eab8e65192c730bf50b41e2adb81b50fb4ce","tid":626151,"uid":96964,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:57:10.000Z","msg":"不停講 講到似層層"},{"pid":"192129cd670a4052c69599a39c7d9a7dce279f42","tid":626151,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":26,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:57:12.000Z","msg":"中波先"},{"pid":"2e925a88c90b86aae64731ea9856a79bdb0db43e","tid":626151,"uid":145365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192129cd670a4052c69599a39c7d9a7dce279f42","tid":626151,"uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":26,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:57:12.000Z","msg":"中波先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"後面隻手禁左下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91db3cba54b84b92129acc64b41ddf4226c392e1